    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="粒子特效（powermode）"><a href="#粒子特效（powermode）" class="headerlink" title="粒子特效（powermode）"></a>粒子特效（powermode）</h3><h4 id="下载"><a href="#下载" class="headerlink" title="下载"></a>下载</h4><p>在插件中心搜索并下载</p><h4 id="配置"><a href="#配置" class="headerlink" title="配置"></a>配置</h4><p>在首选项中打开setting.json（可以通过搜索找到）</p><figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// power mode</span></span><br><span class="line">&quot;powermode.enabled&quot;:true,// 这个必须打开，默认样式的话，只配置这个就行了</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 特效，只能选择一个打开，</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 粒子</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// &quot;powermode.presets&quot;: &quot;particles&quot;,</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 时间间隔</span></span><br><span class="line">&quot;powermode.comboTimeout&quot;: 0,</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 抖动</span></span><br><span class="line">&quot;powermode.enableShake&quot;: false,</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//样式</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 火焰</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// &quot;powermode.presets&quot;: &quot;flames&quot;,</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 炸裂</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// &quot;powermode.presets&quot;: &quot;exploding-rift&quot;,</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 爆炸</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// &quot;powermode.presets&quot;: &quot;simple-rift&quot;,</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 粒子</span></span><br><span class="line">&quot;powermode.presets&quot;: &quot;particles&quot;,</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 烟花</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// &quot;powermode.presets&quot;: &quot;fireworks&quot;,</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 魔法</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// &quot;powermode.presets&quot;: &quot;magic&quot;,</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 回形针</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// &quot;powermode.presets&quot;: &quot;clippy&quot;,</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 其他设置</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 时间间隔</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// &quot;powermode.comboTimeout&quot;: 0,</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 抖动，默认为true</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// &quot;powermode.enableShake&quot;: false,</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// &quot;powermode.enableShake&quot;: true,</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 随字体颜色变化</span></span><br><span class="line">&quot;powermode.backgroundMode&quot;: &quot;mask&quot;,// 这个我设置了感觉没啥用</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
