    <title>搭建个人博客博客（hexo+gitee）</title>
    <link href="https://gitee.com/nciao/myblog/2020/12/29/%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%EF%BC%88hexo-gitee%EF%BC%89/"/>
    <id>https://gitee.com/nciao/myblog/2020/12/29/%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%EF%BC%88hexo-gitee%EF%BC%89/</id>
    <published>2020-12-29T15:10:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-12-29T15:13:39.952Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="个人博客板块（hexo-github）"><a href="#个人博客板块（hexo-github）" class="headerlink" title="个人博客板块（hexo+github）"></a>个人博客板块（hexo+github）</h2><h3 id="准备"><a href="#准备" class="headerlink" title="准备"></a>准备</h3><p>node<br>npm<br>cnpm</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -g cnpm --registry=https://registry.npm.taobao.org</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>hexo</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">// 安装hexo</span><br><span class="line">cnpm install -g hexo-cli</span><br><span class="line">// 查看版本</span><br><span class="line">hexo -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="初始化"><a href="#初始化" class="headerlink" title="初始化"></a>初始化</h3><p>准备一个新文件夹，这里以myblog为例</p><p>在该文件夹下初始化博客</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo init</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>初始化成功会提示</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">INFO  Start blogging with Hexo!</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="启动博客"><a href="#启动博客" class="headerlink" title="启动博客"></a>启动博客</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo server</span><br><span class="line">// 简写</span><br><span class="line">hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>成功得到以下提示</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">INFO  Validating config</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Start processing</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Hexo is running at http://localhost:4000 . Press Ctrl+C to stop.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="新建博客"><a href="#新建博客" class="headerlink" title="新建博客"></a>新建博客</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new &#x27;title&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">// 简写</span><br><span class="line">hexo n &#x27;title&#x27;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h3 id="清理再生成"><a href="#清理再生成" class="headerlink" title="清理再生成"></a>清理再生成</h3><p>在根目录下清理</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>再生成博客内容</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo generate</span><br><span class="line">// 简写</span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>重启服务</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>应该是新建博客才需要重新生成，在帖子里修改的内容，刷新帖子后就能看到改变</p><h3 id="部署到gitee上"><a href="#部署到gitee上" class="headerlink" title="部署到gitee上"></a>部署到gitee上</h3><p>在gitee上新建仓库</p><p>仓库名称与路径一致</p><p><img src="C:\Users\Truthy\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20201228233112969.png" alt="image-20201228233112969"></p><p>重要的是仓库地址，仓库地址与路径相关</p><p>回到终端安装插件</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cnpm i --save hexo-deployer-git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>更改配置<code>_config.yml</code>文件，直接拉到底部，将type的值改为git，将repo改为上面的仓库地址，</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> Deployment</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="comment"># Docs: https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment</span></span></span><br><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">  type: &#x27;&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">// 改成如下</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> Deployment</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="comment"># Docs: https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment</span></span></span><br><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">  type: git</span><br><span class="line">  repo: https://nciao.gitee.io/myblog # 仓库地址</span><br><span class="line">  branch: master # 默认就为master</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>部署到远端</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在对应仓库的导航栏中选择服务，部署网页，成功后该页面会更新出网页的地址</p><p>每次更改页面内容都需要执行    清理&gt;生成&gt;提交&gt;更新部署    这四个流程</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line">hexo d</span><br><span class="line">// 最后在码云对应仓库的服务中更新部署</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="更换主题"><a href="#更换主题" class="headerlink" title="更换主题"></a>更换主题</h3><p>找到目标主题，以butterfly主题为例，一般在作者的github上也有教程。</p><p>在终端的博客根目录下克隆该主题</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git clone -b master https://github.com/jerryc127/hexo-theme-butterfly.git themes/butterfly</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>下载成功后可以在theme文件夹中找到bytterfly文件夹</p><p>接下来在根目录下更改配置文件config.yml</p><p>找到theme，将theme的值改为对应主题名，这里是butterfly</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> Extensions</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="comment"># Plugins: https://hexo.io/plugins/</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="comment"># Themes: https://hexo.io/themes/</span></span></span><br><span class="line">theme: butterfly</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>执行更新流程，更新网页就能看到新主题了</p><h4 id="bug"><a href="#bug" class="headerlink" title="bug"></a>bug</h4><h5 id="重新部署后，页面没有css样式"><a href="#重新部署后，页面没有css样式" class="headerlink" title="重新部署后，页面没有css样式"></a>重新部署后，页面没有css样式</h5><p>查看报错信息，发现页面请求的样式资源未找到，所以应该是静态资源的请求路径有问题，在_config.yml文件中更改如下配置</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">// 默认配置如下</span><br><span class="line">url: http://example.com/child</span><br><span class="line">root: /</span><br><span class="line">// 改为对应的仓库地址</span><br><span class="line">url: https://gitee.com/nciao/myblog</span><br><span class="line">root: /myblog</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>重新部署网页</p><h5 id="更换部分主题后，提示extends-includes-layout-pug-block-content-include-includes-recent-posts-pug-include"><a href="#更换部分主题后，提示extends-includes-layout-pug-block-content-include-includes-recent-posts-pug-include" class="headerlink" title="更换部分主题后，提示extends includes/layout.pug block content include includes/recent-posts.pug include"></a>更换部分主题后，提示extends includes/layout.pug block content include includes/recent-posts.pug include</h5><p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_44318830/article/details/104884936">https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_44318830/article/details/104884936</a></p><p>以下是官方的解决办法</p><p>If you don’t have pug &amp; stylus renderer, try this:</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-renderer-pug hexo-renderer-stylus</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>安装成功后重新部署</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
